§Adding a Stop Motion Image
§22
]TEXTFIELDS§
§TAGS[
§Stop Motion Image; stop motion picture; Image Series; GIF; Camera; Webcam; Paste from Clipboard; move up; move image up; move down; move image down; draft mode; draft tab
